Skeleton warlords can be found in the Ancient Cavern, which is accessible from the Baxtorian Falls. One is found at the north end of the cavern near the Brutal green dragons and waterfiends, while a second is upstairs at the end of the Mithril dragon chamber.

As with all undead, they are weak to the Salve amulet as well as the Salve amulet (e).
